                                  <td colspan="3" align="left" valign="top" class="font10"><ul>
                                    <li >
                                      <div align="justify"><strong>PayPal</strong> - make payments direct to  our PayPal account using your local credit card (Visa, MasterCard, American  Express, Discover and PayPal). <strong>Your  local currency will be reflected to your credit card statement instead of US$.</strong></div>
                                    </li>
                                    <li style="padding-top:10px;">
                                      <div align="justify"><strong>Net Banking</strong> - Make payments through  net-banking using your debit card or through bank account number.<br />
                                        For Bank Details <a href="index.php?object=30" target="_blank"><strong style="text-decoration:underline;">Click here</strong></a></div>
                                    </li>
                                    <li style="padding-top:10px;">
                                      <div align="justify"><strong>Cheque deposit</strong> - You can send a Cheque to  our mailing address or deposit it at any branch of AXIS Bank all over India  nearby you in favor of our account <strong>SQ  Jeans</strong> (Surat). This option can be used by Indian customers only. Send us an  E-mail informing the cheque number, your bank name, branch and the AXIS Bank  branch where you deposit cheque. After clearing of your cheque, we will start  to process your order. <br />
                                        For Bank Details <a href="index.php?object=30" target="_blank"><strong style="text-decoration:underline;">Click here</strong></a></div>
